text: Dede Dekaj (born 20 February 1970), is a former Albanian weightlifter who competed at the 1992 Summer Olympic Games, he finished 9th .Sports-Reference Profile ==References== Category:Weightlifters at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic weightlifters of Albania Category:Living people Category:1970 births Category:Albanian male weightlifters Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
